                        <img src="images/homepage/icons/drop.png" style="width:15px;height:15px;margin-left: 10px;"> 12%
                    </p>
                    <div style="width:100%;background-color: #0099ff;">
                        <p style="text-align: center;width: 100%;font-family: Montserrat;color: white;">Covered</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    style="width:180px;height:250px;border-radius: 0 25px 25px 0 ;background-color: white;margin-right:3px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;">
                    <p style="width:100%;text-align: center;font-family: Montserrat;color:#1d3062;font-size: 18px;"> FRI
